content: That's really helpful, thanks! Speaking of meeting new people, I actually met a new personal trainer at the gym a few days ago who was giving out free consultations. We talked about my fitness goals and she showed me some exercises to help me achieve them. I was impressed by her knowledge and enthusiasm, so I ended up signing up for a few sessions with her. She's been checking in with me daily to see how my progress is going. Do you have any recommendations for staying active and healthy while I'm in Sydney?
